     * LOGIN ACTION TYPES

    LOGIN_ERROR: "LOGIN_ERROR",
  
    /**
     * SIGNUP ACTION TYPES
     */
    SIGN_UP_START: "SIGN_UP_START",
    SIGN_UP_SUCCESS: "SIGN_UP_SUCCESS",
    SIGN_UP_ERROR: "SIGN_UP_ERROR",


    /**
     * SEARCH ACTION TYPES

     USERS_SEARCH_START: "USERS_SEARCH_START",
